title: To become bowl eligible, Cal must limit UCLA QB Josh Rosen
text:

In summer 2013, a burgeoning quarterback recruit from Southern California visited Cal’s pads-less football camp. The Bears’ staff recognized in him the foundation of an elite Pac-12 player: the strong arm, the field vision, the mature approach.
